Robert Adair (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Adair_(actor) 0 Robert Adair (3 January 1900 – 9 August 1954) was an American-born British actor. He was born in San Francisco. Adair died of leukemia in London. Robert_Adair ( 3_January_1900 – 9_August_1954 ) was an_American-born_British_actor . He was_born in San_Francisco . Adair died of leukemia in London .
